"Open Cutling automatically when you sign in." = "Åbn Cutling automatisk, når du logger ind.";
"Accessibility access" = "Tilgængelighedsadgang";
"Granted. Cutling can paste directly into other apps." = "Tildelt. Cutling kan indsætte direkte i andre apps.";
"Lets Cutling paste a cutling straight into the app you were using." = "Lader Cutling indsætte en cutling direkte i den app, du brugte.";
"Grant" = "Tildel";
